App Name: Recipes | Brian Lau | 8/31/2015

Recipes is an application that allows you to organize recipes, ingredients, and categories.

Application Instructions:
1. Visit the website https://recipes-list.herokuapp.com/
2. Add a recipe
3. Add ingredients and categories
4. Add ingredients and categories to recipe
5. Enjoy your new recipes app.

Set Up Instructions:
1. git clone https://github.com/blau08/recipes_test.git
2. bundle
3. rake db:create
4. rake db:migrate
5. ruby app.rb

About:
This product uses a postgresql database to handle and save the data that is entered. It is deployed using Heroku and uses Ruby, ActiveRecord, HTML, and CSS.
